502
00:42:47,029 --> 00:42:48,964
<i>Just sit down.</i>

503
00:42:55,003 --> 00:42:57,337
<i>- Tony--
- Just sit down.</i>

504
00:42:57,406 --> 00:42:59,737
<i>Listen, you son of a bitch!
