505
00:42:59,807 --> 00:43:02,472
<i>Goddamn it, I'll kill ya!</i>

506
00:43:02,546 --> 00:43:04,205
- Stop it!
- Stay the hell away from me!

507
00:43:04,280 --> 00:43:06,543
- Will you cool it!
- Keep him away from me!

508
00:43:06,616 --> 00:43:10,179
<i>- Just get him away from me!
- Can't you just stop it?</i>

509
00:43:10,255 --> 00:43:14,124
<i>I mean, you're hurting your wife!
