510
00:43:14,191 --> 00:43:16,124
<i>I'm so sorry.</i>

511
00:43:17,493 --> 00:43:19,430
<i>I'm- I'm so sorry.</i>

512
00:43:21,563 --> 00:43:24,467
See this?

